and i'm not gonna be ungrateful nor will i complain. Coz I love this. And I think it's everything Blinks needed and expected.

I feel like in this video and choreo... RosÃ© was made to hold back a bit. And that's oke when it's a group and to allow others to shine. But I expect YG to come with something different next month, something where this time RosÃ© is able to show everyone her full potential! Just imagine BP (from debut till now) without RosÃ© for a second....and you'll instantly realize that would create an irreplacable gap that would take away an essential part of BP's uniqueness, sound and valued connection with (international -espescially western- ) fans/BLINKS!!! 
+ keep in mind that many BLINKS aren't K-pop fans/listeners at all, and only love BLACKPINK. That's coz the music and the 4 girls bringing it
